    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Lures:</strong> Small Rapalas, Panther Martins, and Mepps spinners
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Accessories:</strong> Waders, polarized sunglasses, landing net
    </li>
</ul>
<p>
    Always check the conditions and match your gear to the river or lake you plan to fish.
</p>
<h3>
